M_FNOTE[46] = "這裡的“hatthapāsa”復註解釋為十二肘尺之內－  “<b>Hatthapāse</b>ti  idaṃ dvādasahatthaṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ, tasmā  dvādasahatthabbhantare ṭhitaṃ “iman”ti vatvā  adhiṭṭhātabbaṃ. Tato paraṃ “etan”ti vatvā  adhiṭṭhātabbanti keci vadanti.  ”（SārṬ.ii,p.388.）";
